---
title: Honey Garlic Shrimp Wraps with Spiced Sweet Potato Wedges and Ranch
description: Honey garlic sauce – so savoury-sweet it can't be beat! This sauce goes perfectly with crusted and pan-fried shrimp, wrapped together with fresh greens and carrots in soft tortillas and dolloped with creamy ranch. Getting in those Omega-3s has never been this easy!
